title: It feels good to be home! Res Lease in Austin. 2 Beds, 2 Baths
posting_body: ['Come and tour this lovely 1-story 2-bedroom, 2-bathrooms home in ATX!!', "Located on a quiet street, in one of Austin's premier neighborhoods, just a short drive to UT, the Arboretum, and the Domain.", 'With a great floor plan, rustic tiled flooring in the living, dining and kitchen areas and laminated wood flooring in bedrooms, this home will be easy to keep clean.', "You'll love the living room, which has built-in shelves and huge windows that let in the natural light.", 'An open kitchen with a connected dining area offers beautiful views and easy access to the backyard.', "You'll find plenty of counter space, and will enjoy the elegant wood cabinetry and stainless appliances.", 'The luminous and cozy main bedroom comes with a full bath with neutral finishes, white wood cabinetry and a walk-in tiled shower.', 'Be sure to check out the quaint front garden and private backyard with beautiful, shade-giving trees, that are perfect for hosting events.', "A must see, tour and apply today before it's gone!!", '**Gardener included in rent', '**', 'All renters are enrolled in the resident benefits package', '**', 'In person tour required (no exceptions)', '--to set up a viewing--', 'Call/Text/Email ANYTIME!', 'Cristian Argueta', 'show contact info', '(ask for ID# 5677456)', 'All City Real Estate Company', 'Have other properties available....', '(Houses, Duplexes, Apartments, Condos, All Areas)', 'Please be Aware of SCAMS...', 'Do NOT reply to this ad, please call/text for a fast response.', 'Listed By: Benjamin Doherty, Sunroom Rentals Texas, LLC']
